Object Mappers

Disclaimer

Tests on Object Mappers are newer than DI framework tests and so can be inaccurate.

Please do not rely on these and do point any mistakes or inconsistencies.

Collections (read-only property)

Having collections as read-only property is a basic .NET design guideline (even object initializers support it).
It is easy to disregard for DTOs. However, the mapper can be used for mapping to proper domain objects as well.

Name AutoMapper EasyMapper EmitMapper fFastMapper Fpr Meow.Cartograph OoMapper ThisMember ValueInjecter
IList ⇒ IList fail fail fail fail fail fail fail fail fail
ICollection ⇒ ICollection fail fail fail fail fail fail fail fail fail
ISet ⇒ ISet fail fail fail fail fail fail fail fail fail
